1. Stojim na ivici ponora i strah me hvata. (*ivici*) (I am standing on the edge of the abyss and I am afraid.)
2. Ogradili su park sa ivicima od crnog granita. (*ivicima*) (They fenced the park with black granite edges.)
3. Ivici torte su ukrašeni šlagom i voćem. (*Ivici*) (The edges of the cake are decorated with whipped cream and fruit.)
4. Voda se slila niz ivice krova i napravila jezerce ispod. (*ivice*) (Water flowed down the edges of the roof and formed a small lake below.)
5. Ivicama ceste treba posvetiti više pažnje kako bi se spriječile nesreće. (*Ivicama*) (More attention should be paid to the edges of the road to prevent accidents.)